                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-17-defend198 t17930410-17-punish95"></join>
               Imprisoned six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Lord KENYON.</p>
